ockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係簽左offer letter(都姐係contract la?),<br />\n佢冇講effective date- 只係話employment will commence second half of 2017 and employment may be terminated by giving one month written notice. If short notice is agreed, full compensation must be paid. <br />\n<br />\n係咪姐係11/9返工，11/8 之前要reject 呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHR緊係唔番啦<br />\n不過你照腥啦 佢其實見你no show都知咩事<br />\n好平常，成日都有candidate咁架啦"},{"pid":"00f6fe0a0e7f30a2fc925832d3b1bf6751eb169e","tid":392648,"uid":67867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T01:51:45.000Z","msg":"一簽左就已經effective啦<br />\n當resign喇"},{"pid":"05b3ce335f6916f87ea39b9c642b9a962cb1e7df","tid":392648,"uid":26200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:04:38.000Z","msg":"正路effective date應該係返工第一日<br />\n任何原因令你第一日返唔到工張contract就無效<br />\n好似係 睇下有冇做hr嘅解答下"},{"pid":"b1517ec4884e895b8dadef0d9692e299ce981756","tid":392648,"uid":132679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T08:14:07.000Z","msg":"Thanks brothers/sisters們<br />\n有冇hr/過來人 解答下<br />\n感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd30787c13f14125f1ec7de20879a7f0dca1160","tid":392648,"uid":128010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:37:10.000Z","msg":"睇人工做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}